sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Op as Operator (Power Admin)
    participant Main as Main Server
    participant BE3 as Backup Node BE-3
    participant Cat as BackupSnapshotCatalog
    participant Job as BackupRestoreJob
    participant BE6 as Primary Worker BE-6
    participant PriDB as Primary App-DB

    Op->>Main: Request restore (PairingId, SnapshotDate)
    Main->>BE3: POST /API/V1/Backup/RestoreByDate (S2S, scope Backup.Restore.Write)
    BE3->>Cat: Lookup snapshot for date
    alt Not found
        BE3-->>Main: 404 MAIN-830-01 SnapshotNotFound
    else In progress
        BE3-->>Main: 409 MAIN-830-02 RestoreAlreadyInProgress
    else Found
        BE3->>Job: Enqueue RestoreJob (Status=Pending)
        BE3-->>Main: 202 Accepted { RestoreJobId }

        Job->>Job: Decrypt snapshot zip (HKDF "BackupSnapshot/v1")
        Job->>Job: Re-seal under current Active KeyEpoch (forward secrecy)
        Job->>BE6: POST /API/V1/Backup/RestoreInbox (scope Backup.Restore.Apply)
        BE6->>PriDB: Offline App-tier import (bypass Stage-4 dispatch)
        PriDB->>PriDB: Reset BackupSyncWatermark = MaxSyncOpSeq(snapshot)
        BE6-->>Job: 200 OK
        Job->>Job: Status=Completed
    end

    Note over Job,PriDB: Restore success realigns watermark — subsequent BE-1 deliveries resume cleanly.
